**User Profiles Management** is a responsive web application built using **React (Vite)** and **Tailwind CSS**.  
It allows users to **create, edit, delete, search, and manage user profiles** with persistent data stored in the browserâ€™s **localStorage** â€” all without requiring a backend server.

This project demonstrates front-end CRUD operations, state management using React hooks, and local persistence using browser storage.

